title: Guy Branum on Party Girl
itunes:title: Guy Branum on Party Girl
description:
Guy Branum is a pure delight. Chuck had a blast sitting down with him in the home studio to talk about his movie crush, the 90s indie darling, Party Girl. The talk went so well, Chuck wanted to start another podcast with Guy. A guy can dream, after all.
